room_title: Escape room "The Quest for the Sword" by 321 Escape Rooms in Melbourne
room_address: 5270 N US HWY 1 Palm Shores, FL 32940
room_description: Merlin is in search of one worthy to be the ruler of our great land. He has invited members of the noblest families of the kingdom to participate in a tournament. Join with other defenders of the realm and see if you have what it takes to discover the sword Merlin has hidden and unsheathe it from its rock!
